}
let email = builder
    .subject(&subject)
    .multipart(body)
    .context("failed to build email message")?;
```

Context:
- Uses the `lettre` crate for email building/sending
- `addr.parse()` produces a `lettre::message::Mailbox`
- `Message::builder().to(mailbox)` can be called multiple times to add multiple To: recipients
- All recipients will see each other's addresses in the To: header

Please identify any real issues.

